Compilation info
The Best Jazz...Ever!
Label: Circa Records Ltd.
Catalog#: VTCD 93
Format: 3 x CD
Country: UK

This is the comp that really got me into jazz. All the greats are here; nothing a jazz buff wouldn't have but if you want someone to get into the jazz, this is the comp to give them. Anyone who doesn't like Disc 1 must be deaf.

b]Tracklist[/b]
1-01 Nat King Cole & George Shearing - Let There Be Love
1-02 Ella Fitzgerald - I Get A Kick Out Of You
1-03 Dinah Washington - Mad About The Boy
1-04 Peggy Lee - Fever
1-05 Julie London - Cry Me A River
1-06 Billie Holiday - That Ole Devil Called Love
1-07 Duke Ellington - Take The 'A' Train
1-08 Cab Calloway - Minnie The Moocher
1-09 Louis Jordan - Five Guys Named Moe
1-10 Louis Armstrong - Hello Dolly
1-11 Fats Waller - Ain't Misbehavin'
1-12 Leon Redbone - Relax
1-13 Sarah Vaughan - Summertime
1-14 Erroll Garner - Misty
1-15 Barney Kessel - A Foggy Day
1-16 Django Reinhardt - Night And Day
1-17 Chet Baker - Let's Get Lost
1-18 Billy Taylor Trio - I Wish I Knew (How It Would Feel To Be Free)
1-19 Count Basie - The Kid From Red Bank
1-20 Dave Brubeck Quartet, The - Take Five

2-01 Weather Report - Birdland
2-02 Roy Ayers - Running Away
2-03 Mongo Santamaria - Watermelon Man
2-04 Georgie Fame - Moondance Featuring - Jon Hendricks
2-05 Mose Allison - Do Nothing Till You Hear From Me
2-06 Ramsey Lewis Trio, The - Wade In The Water
2-07 Style Council, The - Dropping Bombs On The Whitehouse
2-08 Al Jarreau - (Round, Round, Round) Blue Ronda A La Turke
2-09 Ronny Jordan - So What
2-10 George Benson - Breezin'
2-11 Spyro Gyra - Morning Dance
2-12 Randy Crawford - Last Night At Danceland
2-13 State Of The Heart - The Girl From Ipanema
2-14 Pat Metheny - Travels

3-01 Miles Davis - So What
3-02 Herbie Hancock - Cantaloupe Island
3-03 Thelonious Monk - Round Midnight
3-04 Horace Silver - Song For My Father
3-05 Lee Morgan - The Sidewinder
3-06 Art Blakey - Moanin'
3-07 Kenny Burrell - Midnight Blue
3-08 Stanley Jordan - Eleanor Rigby
3-09 Charles Mingus - Goodbye Pork Pie Hat
3-10 Charlie Parker - Ornithology
3-11 John Coltrane - Blue Train
